OL,3,CHow relatives of Israeli hostages
OL,4,Cfound unexpected community in the UK
OL,6,FWords by Khadija Kothia, ITV News
OL,7,FProducer
OL,9,FFor the families of Israeli hostages
OL,10,Fliving in the UK, the past fifteen
OL,11,Fmonths have been heavy with loss,
OL,12,Funcertainty and mourning. In its
OL,13,Fplace, they have found an unexpected
OL,14,Fform of comfort and solace through
OL,15,Fcommunity.
