OL,3,CHow relatives of Israeli hostages
OL,4,Cfound unexpected community in the UK
OL,6,FTottenham Hotspur football fans
OL,7,Fchanted in support of 28-year-old
OL,8,FBritish-Israeli hostage and Spurs
OL,9,Fsupporter Emily Damari while yellow
OL,10,Fribbons became a symbol of support for
OL,11,Fthe hostages worn across the nation.
OL,13,FElsewhere, campaigners advocating for
OL,14,Fthe release of 24-year-old Romi Gonen
OL,15,Fwore her favourite leopard print
OL,16,Fpattern when attending vigils.
