OL,3,CHow relatives of Israeli hostages
OL,4,Cfound unexpected community in the UK
OL,6,F"We really appreciate the sentiment,"
OL,7,FAdam Ma'anit told ITV News. His 50-
OL,8,Fyear-old cousin Tsachi Idan is still
OL,9,Fin captivity, though his family are
OL,10,Funsure about whether he is alive.
OL,12,FHamas captured 251 people on 7 October
OL,13,F2023 in a surprise attack that killed
OL,14,F1,195 Israelis, resulting in a 15
OL,15,Fmonth ground invasion of Gaza and a
OL,16,Freported 46,000 deaths by Israel.
OL,18,FThree female Israeli hostages were
OL,19,Freleased by Hamas on 19 January 2025,
OL,20,Fmarking the first phase of the new
OL,21,Fceasefire deal.
