OL,3,CHow relatives of Israeli hostages
OL,4,Cfound unexpected community in the UK
OL,6,FEmily Damari, 28, was one of these
OL,7,Freleased hostages.
OL,9,F"We are just in shock, elated," says
OL,10,FTony Moss, Emily's second cousin
OL,11,Fliving in Radlett, England. "We feel
OL,12,Fjoy, but this is just the beginning."
OL,14,FUpon seeing Damari waving her bandaged
OL,15,Fhand as she was released, Adam found
OL,16,Fsupport from a random interaction with
OL,17,F'an amazing Jewish woman in Ireland'
OL,18,Fon social media site X.
