OL,3,CHow relatives of Israeli hostages
OL,4,Cfound unexpected community in the UK
OL,6,FBut family connections have not been
OL,7,Fthe only way that Britons have found
OL,8,Frelation to the hostages.
OL,10,FHundreds of yellow balloons were
OL,11,Freleased into the air during Tottenham
OL,12,FHotspur's football match against
OL,13,FNewcastle United on 6 January 2025 in
OL,14,Fsupport of Damari.
OL,16,F'She's one of our own, she's one of
OL,17,Four own, Emily Damari, bring her home'
OL,18,Fbecame a regular chant among Spurs
OL,19,Fsupporters.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
