OL,3,CHow relatives of Israeli hostages
OL,4,Cfound unexpected community in the UK
OL,6,FAn image of Damari holding a Spurs
OL,7,Fscarf was even released by the Israeli
OL,8,Fambassador to the UK soon after her
OL,9,Frelease, with a caption on X saying
OL,10,Fthat Damari had 'sent her heartfelt
OL,11,Fgratitude (to) the Spurs fans for all
OL,12,Ftheir incredible support during her
OL,13,Ftime in captivity' as they 'never gave
OL,14,Fup hope'.
OL,16,F"It is interesting how much of the fan
OL,17,Fbase has actually really helped us in
OL,18,Fterms of feeling less alone and
OL,19,Fsupported," Adam Ma'anit says.
