OL,3,CHow relatives of Israeli hostages
OL,4,Cfound unexpected community in the UK
OL,6,FThe campaigners found that football
OL,7,Fbecame a way to help connect people to
OL,8,FEmily's story.
OL,10,F"A lot of people think Israelis as
OL,11,Fthese foreigners but then they hear
OL,12,FEmily was a Spurs fan," Adam says.
OL,14,F"Suddenly, that humanises her and a
OL,15,Flot of people could relate to her."
OL,17,FThe campaign also tied the families of
OL,18,Fhostages in the UK together, forming a
OL,19,Fsense of familiarity and community
OL,20,Fthrough their shared loss.
