OL,3,CHow relatives of Israeli hostages
OL,4,Cfound unexpected community in the UK
OL,6,F"Emily was a very strong part of my
OL,7,Flife the last 15 months," Adam says.
OL,9,F"I've not met her, but I feel like I
OL,10,Fknow her, because I've learned so
OL,11,Fmuch."
OL,13,F"I've seen all of those photos. I've
OL,14,Fseen her dog. I've met Mandy, her
OL,15,Fmother and her uncle. I just feel so
OL,16,Fconnected."
OL,18,FWhile the families have found
OL,19,Fconnection through loss, captivity
OL,20,Fmarked a rupture in connection for the
OL,21,Fhostages.
