OL,3,CHow relatives of Israeli hostages
OL,4,Cfound unexpected community in the UK
OL,6,FEmily learned upon release from
OL,7,Fcaptivity that her grandfather had
OL,8,Fdied, while Tsachi's wife Gali Idan
OL,9,Fhas been unable to visit the grave of
OL,10,Fher 18-year-old daughter Ma'ayan who
OL,11,Fwas shot by Hamas while helping her
OL,12,Ffather protect their family.
OL,14,F"She can't properly grieve because
OL,15,Fshe's still stuck in the moment. She's
OL,16,Fwaiting for her other half to come
OL,17,Fback," Adam says.
OL,19,F"It's really tough."
