OL,3,CHow relatives of Israeli hostages
OL,4,Cfound unexpected community in the UK
OL,6,FTony says that Emily's mother Mandy
OL,7,Fwaited 15 months for just one hug from
OL,8,Fher daughter.
OL,10,F"Emily used to have a 42 second hug
OL,11,Fwith her mother everyday," he says.
OL,13,F"They say it takes 40 seconds for the
OL,14,Fdopamine to be released to get the
OL,15,Freal benefit for the hug."
OL,17,F"That was the thing she (Mandy) was
OL,18,Flooking forward to. She did not know
OL,19,Fshe would have another one."
