OL,3,CHow relatives of Israeli hostages
OL,4,Cfound unexpected community in the UK
OL,6,FFor those released or due to be
OL,7,Freleased under phase one of the deal,
OL,8,Fsuch as Tsachi, life will have to be
OL,9,Frebuilt once again.
OL,11,FFor those who didn't qualify for
OL,12,Frelease under phase one, such as Omri
OL,13,FMiran, a gardener and shiatsu teacher
OL,14,Fwhose brother-in-law Adam became close
OL,15,Fto after the attack, their families
OL,16,Fremain even more uncertain.
OL,18,FTony says he feels Emily's release is
OL,19,F'bittersweet' given that the majority
OL,20,Fof hostages have not yet been released.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
