OL,3,CHow relatives of Israeli hostages
OL,4,Cfound unexpected community in the UK
OL,6,FFor Adam, Emily's release provides
OL,7,Fhope.
OL,9,F"We kind of just use this moment as
OL,10,Ffuel to enjoy and to feel the joy as a
OL,11,Fsense of possibility that this could
OL,12,Fhappen to us too," Adam says.
OL,14,F"We needed some good news, and this is
OL,15,Fgood news."
